        "TileImage": "$($repository 836418b0-1a76-44e0-ba31-fd8b0f2a1bce).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Haven is covertly engineering The Apex Serum, a bio-weapon designed to overwrite free will with elite combat instincts. The targets are Haven employees serving as unsuspecting hosts for this sleeper agent protocol. If they live, the serum will activate, turning them into lethal assassins that rival your own skills. Eliminate these individuals before they are sold to the highest bidder. Neutralize the threat before the Apex reaches its final stage.",
